      "description": "Usable fair-condition car that should suit someone looking for a driver-level example rather than a showpiece. It presents decently overall but shows visible age, wear, and cosmetic imperfections inside and out, with finishes, trim, and interior materials reflecting regular use. Buyers should expect an older vehicle that may benefit from continued sorting, detailing, or light refurbishment depending on their standards, but it should still appeal to someone wanting an honest, reasonably presentable car at a more approachable price.",
